	                     "**tankgirl** - Get a random tankgirl.\n\n"+
	                     "\n__**Help:**__\n"+
	                     "**@" + client.user.username + " help** - Display this help message.\n"+
	                     "**@" + client.user.username + " aliases DM** - Send a DM with a list of tag aliases.\n"+
